main event: A radar observation of a round-shaped object with flashing lights was reported on 13 October 1956.
interesting points: The object emitted red, green, and white flashing lights,The sighting lasted between 0 to 1 minute,The object was seen moving slowly,The observer suspected the object might be a balloon,There were no photographs included in the report.
sighted object: one round-shaped object with flashing lights
